## Exception Handling

### Legitimate Research Limitations
**Time Constraints**: When episode deadline requires abbreviated research
**Topic Novelty**: When covering very recent releases with limited analysis available
**Niche Topics**: When specific expertise is scarce

**Exception Process**:
1. Document limitation reason
2. Implement mitigation strategy (extended personal analysis, future episode correction)
3. Transparently disclose limitation to audience
4. Plan follow-up research for future episodes

